- crates/axon-storage/src/memory.rs — add impl
- crates/axon-storage/src/sqlite.rs — add impl
- crates/axon-storage/src/postgres.rs — add impl
- crates/axon-server/src/lib.rs — pub mod federation
- crates/axon-server/src/federation.rs — NEW file with resolve_tailscale_identity
- crates/axon-server/tests/federation_test.rs — NEW test file

## Files NOT to touch

- crates/axon-server/src/auth.rs — legacy Tailscale path, leave it alone
- crates/axon-server/src/auth_pipeline.rs — B1's JWT pipeline; B3 is parallel, not an extension
- crates/axon-core/src/auth.rs — types are done, do not extend

